<h2 id="preparation">Preparation</h2>

<p>Here are the steps to cook the meal. Takes as long as it takes. Share and enjoy!</p>

<ol>
  <li>Play music in the kitchen. <a href="">I recommend this playlist.</a></li>
  <li>Pore a glass of drink for the chef.</li>
  <li>Preheat a sauce pan, and pore the oats in.</li>
  <li>Add the sultanas, and wait a few minutes until the oats start to roast.</li>
  <li>Now add the cup of milk, and let the oats absorb it.</li>
  <li>Add the cup of water and let it absorb but keep it runny enough.</li>
  <li>Add the sugar and stir for a minute.</li>
  <li>Serve with a tsp of strawberry jam on top.</li>
</ol>
